graph TD
    %% User Inputs
    User([User / Recruiter])
    JD[Job Description File]
    Resumes[Resume Files PDF/DOCX]
    
    User -->|Uploads| JD
    User -->|Uploads Batch| Resumes

    %% Processing Pipeline
    subgraph FastAPI Backend
        DocParser[Document Parser<br/>PyMuPDF / docx2txt]
        Extractor[LLM Skill Extractor]
        EvalAgent[LLM Evaluator Agent]
        Fallback[TF-IDF Keyword Fallback]
    end

    %% External APIs
    subgraph External APIs
        GitHubAPI[(GitHub API)]
        LLMAPI[(OpenAI API)]
    end

    %% Data Flow
    JD --> DocParser
    Resumes --> DocParser
    DocParser -->|Raw Text| Extractor
    
    Extractor <-->|Extract Links & Entities| LLMAPI
    Extractor -->|GitHub Handle| GitHubAPI
    
    GitHubAPI -->|Commit/Language JSON| EvalAgent
    DocParser -->|Raw Text| EvalAgent
    
    EvalAgent <-->|Structured JSON Scoring| LLMAPI
    
    %% Fallback Logic
    EvalAgent -.->|On Timeout/Error| Fallback
    DocParser -.->|Raw Text| Fallback
    
    %% Output
    EvalAgent --> Output[Ranked JSON Array]
    Fallback --> Output
    Output --> Client[Frontend Result Cards / CSV]
